title: What Eric Andre Has In Common With Fran Lebowitz | Colbert Classic
description:
Eric Andre and Stephen have a bourbon together over Zoom and rave about Tiffany Haddish, his brilliant co-star in "Bad Trip," available now on Netflix. Find out all that Eric Andre has in common with Fran Lebowitz in this charmingly chaotic Colbert Classic!
